Starstomp, with her new beast form, started walking out of the mine's 
remaining rooms. She did not know anything of her current position, but she 
needed to find it out. She scanned the area to the west for any signs at 
long-range of technology. She received a positive signal.

Starstomp:
Alright... To any entity or being, this is an emergency help request 
transmission. My name is Starstomp and I have somehow crashed on this 
planet. I am a cybertronian and I wish to cause no harm. Please reply soon. 
I am almost in stasis lock and I really need help!!!
